Package: geomix
Type: Package
Title: Simultaneous Unmixing of Compositional and Distributional Data for
    Sedimentary Provenance Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Gabriel", "Bertolini",
    email = "gabertol@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides methods for simultaneous unmixing of compositional data
    (e.g., bulk petrology) and continuous distributions (e.g., detrital zircon
    ages) in sedimentary provenance analysis. Uses centered log-ratio (CLR)
    transformation for compositional data and non-negative least squares (NNLS)
    optimization with fair normalization between data blocks. Includes bootstrap
    methods for uncertainty quantification.
